{"tid":2044839,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國外相藍韜文：英國絕對不會放棄對香港的責任","createTime":"2020-05-31T11:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T12:21:01.000Z","uid":53844,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"61b62e0b2aa105457f12a63f0803b41a7aadeda8","tid":2044839,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:13:00.000Z","msg":"全國人大通過「港區國安法」的決定草案，引發國際社會關注。英國外相藍韜文（Dominic Raab）日前表示，若中國不停止訂立國安法，將會更改 BNO 在英國的居留條件，居留期由 6 個月變成 12 個月，又指是為將來取得公民權鋪路。藍韜文今日接受《BBC》訪問時表示，英國不會視而不見，亦不會背棄對香港的責任，重申早前提出延長 BNO 簽證的建議，是回應中國即將在香港實施國家安全法。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文指，如果中國落實港區安全法，便會給予持有 BNO 護照的人來英國的權利，並估計部份人會前往英國（a fraction of them would actually come）。他強調，英國不會對香港視而不見，亦不會背棄英國對香港人的責任。"},{"pid":"d11331e5337dfc34e0a893786c5c1e57ef13578f","tid":2044839,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:14:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cd158cb8a0b93d828c60626115a8040a6e73bbe","tid":2044839,"uid":4574,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:15:22.000Z","msg":"Fai Dee la diu"},{"pid":"4b14d51901fa52ad4492b1f8daf46b121b963411","tid":2044839,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:15:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b07d9c8e277dea7b7c690245b36e5b1c803b8e02","tid":2044839,"uid":103521,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:17:21.000Z","msg":"分化撚肯收皮未? &quot;英國又出賣&quot;, &quot;英國戰線冇用&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b08601c267e0225e855aa8bf108dff843bd40f6","tid":2044839,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:18:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b08a6d352b4d4808ea32af709a5678ebf50e0d0c","tid":2044839,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:21:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1712b0ed64280f58a9e8e89c11e26ec48e3e5ed","tid":2044839,"uid":53844,"like":2,"disli